{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a virus that has infiltrated the System to destroy it. Fight off hordes of antivirus programs.  Evolve, adapt, and fight everyone who gets in your way. Destroy one section of the System after another and cause as much damage as possible. Even if your virus is destroyed, others will replace it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/Untitled2.gif?t=1732318600\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intrude And Destroy</strong> is <i><u>a retro-styled roguelite-FPS</u></i>. You need to shoot enemies and destroy all the objects on the levels. For the former you get experience, which can be spent on upgrades and new weapons. For the second - valuable resources that can be spent on improvements for the next invasions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try this meditative game <i>inspired by the atmosphere of early consoles and FPS-games.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose the picture mode to suit you - retro or clean screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/Untitled1__1_.gif?t=1732318600\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Catch an infection","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297120/cda8323ba8f93915d2f3d5956006b617f4d42064.jpg"},{"name":"Just a Bit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297120/10641a8b74e739205b028c458ff9957a35ad121f.jpg"},{"name":"A Taste of Pixel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297120/0f2825b061fcc5f940cf1ba1356a94febc18ea05.jpg"},{"name":"Bit Machine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297120/358cb8e37f682cd8ec78c6c0e8e3d426dbeb4baa.jpg"},{"name":"Trou